07:54.560 --> 07:56.720
Awak rasa awak cukup istimewa?

08:09.040 --> 08:10.770
Awak nak saya panggil awak apa?

08:11.000 --> 08:11.480
Xia Yi,

08:12.630 --> 08:13.800
Pongsri Leekpa

08:14.430 --> 08:15.160
