08:53.240 --> 08:54.430
Sehari kemudian,

08:54.600 --> 08:56.420
[Penyata Perincian Sejarah Transaksi Akaun
Bank Komersial Bandar Lihai]

08:55.360 --> 08:57.390
akaun bank awak, Lin Huosheng

08:57.390 --> 09:00.030
