14:17.740 --> 14:18.920
Kan saya dah cakap?

14:19.150 --> 14:20.480
Matilah jika tak lari.

14:23.650 --> 14:24.840
Habislah kali ini.

14:25.840 --> 14:26.820
Pengecut.

14:27.080 --> 14:28.360
Awak masih sama macam dahulu,

14:28.360 --> 14:30.000
